Indian Oil Said to Buy 6 Million Barrels of West African Oil

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u
-- 
2011-03-04T16:36:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-04/indian-oil-said-to-buy-6-million-barrels-of-west-african-oil.html
Indian Oil Corp., the nation’s
largest refiner, bought about 6 million barrels of West African  crude oil  for loading in April and May from Royal Dutch Shell
Plc and Vitol Group, three people who participate in the market
said today.  A Shell official declined to comment, asking not to be
identified in line with company policy. Telephone calls to a
London-based Vitol official weren’t answered.  Details of the purchase are as follows:  To contact the reporters on this story:
Sherry Su in London at 
 Lsu23@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
